Connect to VPN & streamstore:
 - openvpn3 session-start --config /etc/openvpn3/client.ovpn
 - cssh -l skalogerakis -p 2222 139.91.183.36 139.91.183.74 139.91.183.133 139.91.183.66 139.91.183.87

Build first the source code locally, branch sk-1.13.1
 - Format the code using: mvn spotless:apply
 - Build the version: mvn clean install -DskipTests -Dcheckstyle.skip -Drat.ignoreErrors=true -Dhadoop.version=3.2.2

Copy from local directory to all streamstore servers:
 - scp -P 2222 -r /home/skalogerakis/flink skalogerakis@139.91.183.66:/media/localdisk/skalogerakis/flink

Modify configurations:
 - Modify flink/bin/config.sh
    - Change the default port on TMWorkers() functions and on ssh -p 2222
 - Modify flink/conf/masters
    - node01:8081 (Master IP)
 - Modify flink/conf/workers
    - Add all workers (node02, node03...)
 - Modify flink/conf/flink-conf.yaml
    - jobmanager.rpc.address: node01
    - // taskmanager.memory.process.size: 1728m
    - taskmanager.memory.flink.size: 20000m
    - state.backend: rocksdb
    -  state.backend.incremental: true
    -  state.checkpoints.dir: hdfs:///flink_checkpoints # location to store checkpoints
    -  state.backend.rocksdb.localdir: /media/localdisk/skalogerakis/tmp/rocksdb	#Store on SSD
    -  io.tmp.dirs: /media/localdisk/skalogerakis/tmp/io	#Store on SSD



